<p><img alt="" class="img-focus" src="https://img3.jiemian.com/101/original/20250126/import_weibo_5126857842233646_a700xH.jpg"/></p>
<!-- 关联公司 --><div class="newsflash-company" id="newsflash-company"></div></div>]]></description><guid isPermaLink="false">12294880</guid><pubDate>Sun, 26 Jan 2025 00:15:18 +0800</pubDate></item><item><title>台湾屏东县发生4.4级地震，震源深度15千米</title><link>https://www.jiemian.com/article/12294885.html</link><description><![CDATA[<div class="article-content"><p>中国地震台网正式测定：01月26日00时10分在台湾屏东县（北纬22.80度，东经120.68度）发生4.4级地震，震源深度15千米。</p>
<p><img alt="" class="img-focus" src="https://img2.jiemian.com/101/original/20250126/import_weibo_5126859503440745_a700xH.jpg"/></p>
